Hair doesn’t have to be perfect. The easiest and quickest way to do a sleeked back bun that doesn’t require you to try to do it over and over again. Don’t be afraid to clip your hair! I have a lot of layers so there’s no way that pomade or gel will just hold it altogether. This is my go-to sleeked back bun when my hair is oily and I have no time to wash & style.
.
.
.
#sleekbun #slickback #oilyhair #easyhairstyles
